==Introduction==
The '''Email Property Type''' represents an email.

The Wiki Automation Tool supports editing, viewing and searching on the Email properties.


==Definition==

The Email Property extends a common definition of the [[Help:Property|Property Definition]] with the following elements:

<pre>

<concept>
  <structure>
    <property name="{PROPERTY NAME}" format="{FORMAT}"/>
  </structure>
</concept>

<properties>
  <property name="{PROPERTY NAME}" ... size={SIZE}>
  </property>
</properties>
</pre>

{| class="helptable"
|-
! {SIZE}
| A length of the input field. Default value: 50.
|-
! {FORMAT}
| A format to be used to display the multi-value fields. The following values are allowed:
* ''bullets'' (default)
* ''commas''
|}


==Semantic database==
The Email Property is implemented as a [[Special:Types/String]] MediaWiki datatype.


==Example==
<pre>
<property name="Email" type="Email" label="Email" attribute="email">
  <description>Email.</description>
</property>
</pre>


==User Interface==
* '''View Page'''
The property displays a text value entered by the user with a link with protocol set to 'mailto'.

* '''Edit Page'''
The property provides one line text input field.
A length of the field is controlled by the 'size' attribute.

* '''Search Page'''
The property allows user to choose a search operator from the following options: ''Starts with, Contains, Equals, Ends with, Has any''
and allows user to enter a desired value in one line text input field.
